HB 685 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Mena
Abstract: Provides for an exception to the public bid law regarding the procurement of
public motor vehicles and rolling stock by allowing state entities to utilize the Fixing
America's Surface Transportation Act (FAST Act).
Present law (R.S. 38:2212(B)) requires public entities within the state of La. to only use the
La. Uniform Bid Form.
Propose law (R.S. 38:2212.11) provides for an exception to the required use of the La.
Uniform Bid Form by allowing public entities to utilize the procurement process provided
in the FAST Act to purchase public motor vehicles and rolling stock and related equipment.
(Adds R.S. 38:2212.11)
